name: [KAVI & JIUN] [HOST COMMUNITY] [PROJECT ONG TU-GETHER] - 1st & 2nd Rejection PN and EDM Automation

parameters.query:
=SET TIMEZONE = 'Asia/Kuala_Lumpur';

select distinct l.id, 
l.registration_no, 
m.name as model,
case when ll.city_id in (1) then '1. KV'   
when ll.city_id in (2,12) then '2. PG'
when ll.city_id in (3,19,20,21) then '3. KK'  
when ll.city_id in (4,15) then '4. JB' 
when ll.city_id in (5) then '5. IP' 
when ll.city_id in (47) then '6. NS'
when ll.city_id in (13) then '7. LGK'
else '8. Others' end as city,
l.user_id, 
concat(u.first_name, ' ',u.last_name)as host_name, 
u.email, 
u.uuid,
u.phone_number,
ola.overall_avai_days,
case when obj.ov_rej_booking is null then '0' else obj.ov_rej_booking end as overall_rej_booking,
case when obj.unfair_rej_booking is null then '0' else obj.unfair_rej_booking end as unfair_rej_booking,
case when obj.real_rej_booking is null then '0' else obj.real_rej_booking end as real_rej_booking,
case when obf.overall_fuld_booking is null then '0' else obf.overall_fuld_booking end as overall_fuld_booking,
case when wbj.ov_rej_booking is null then '0' else wbj.ov_rej_booking end as weekend_overall_rej_booking,
case when wbj.unfair_rej_booking is null then '0' else wbj.unfair_rej_booking end as weekend_unfair_rej_booking,
case when wbj.real_rej_booking is null then '0' else wbj.real_rej_booking end as weekend_real_rej_booking,
wla.weekend_avai_days,
case when wbf.weekend_fuld_booking is null then '0' else wbf.weekend_fuld_booking end as weekend_fuld_booking
from listings l 
left join users u on u.id = l.user_id
left join (select distinct listing_id, country, city_id from listing_location) ll on ll.listing_id = l.id
left join models m on m.id = l.model_id
left join companies c on c.owner_id = l.user_id
--
left join 
        (select distinct b.listing_id, 
        count(distinct case when (b.status = 'rejected' and (b.reason !~* '(guest)' or b.reason is null)) or (b.status in ('withdrawn', 'cancelled') and b.reason ~* '(host|owner|avai|car)') then b.ref_no end) as ov_rej_booking,
		count(distinct case when (b.reason = 'Host is taking a long time to respond' and ((extract(EPOCH FROM b.updated_at::timestamp) - EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM b.created_at::timestamp))/60::integer)< '20' ) then b.ref_no end)as unfair_rej_booking,
		COALESCE(count(distinct case when (b.status = 'rejected' and (b.reason !~* '(guest)' or b.reason is null)) or (b.status in ('withdrawn', 'cancelled') and b.reason ~* '(host|owner|avai|car)') then b.ref_no end) - count(distinct case when (b.reason = 'Host is taking a long time to respond' and ((extract(EPOCH FROM b.updated_at::timestamp) - EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM b.created_at::timestamp))/60::integer)< '20' ) then b.ref_no end),0) as real_rej_booking  
        from bookings b 
        where b.request_end_at::timestamp >= '2023-01-18 00:00' and b.request_start_at::timestamp <= '2023-01-31 23:59'
        group by 1)obj
        on obj.listing_id = l.id
--
left join 
        (select distinct b.listing_id, 
        count(distinct case when (b.status = 'rejected' and (b.reason !~* '(guest)' or b.reason is null)) or (b.status in ('withdrawn', 'cancelled') and b.reason ~* '(host|owner|avai|car)') then b.ref_no end) as ov_rej_booking,
		count(distinct case when (b.reason = 'Host is taking a long time to respond' and ((extract(EPOCH FROM b.updated_at::timestamp) - EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM b.created_at::timestamp))/60::integer)< '20' ) then b.ref_no end)as unfair_rej_booking,
		COALESCE(count(distinct case when (b.status = 'rejected' and (b.reason !~* '(guest)' or b.reason is null)) or (b.status in ('withdrawn', 'cancelled') and b.reason ~* '(host|owner|avai|car)') then b.ref_no end) - count(distinct case when (b.reason = 'Host is taking a long time to respond' and ((extract(EPOCH FROM b.updated_at::timestamp) - EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM b.created_at::timestamp))/60::integer)< '20' ) then b.ref_no end),0) as real_rej_booking
        from bookings b 
        where (b.request_start_at::timestamp between '2023-01-20 00:00' and '2023-01-23 23:59') or (b.request_start_at::timestamp between '2023-01-27 00:00' and '2023-01-29 23:59')
        group by 1)wbj
        on wbj.listing_id = l.id
--
left join 
        (select distinct b.listing_id, 
        count(distinct case when b.status in ('completed','start_driving','waiting_for_inspection', 'return_car','accepted') then b.id end) as overall_fuld_booking
        from bookings b 
        where b.request_end_at::timestamp >= '2023-01-18 00:00' and b.request_start_at::timestamp <= '2023-01-31 23:59'
        group by 1)obf
        on obf.listing_id = l.id
--
left join 
        (select distinct b.listing_id, 
        count(distinct case when b.status in ('completed','start_driving','waiting_for_inspection', 'return_car','accepted') then b.id end) as weekend_fuld_booking
        from bookings b 
        where (b.request_start_at::timestamp between '2023-01-20 00:00' and '2023-01-23 23:59') or (b.request_start_at::timestamp between '2023-01-27 00:00' and '2023-01-29 23:59')
        group by 1)wbf
        on wbf.listing_id = l.id
--
left join 
        (select l.id,
        count(dates.ymd) as overall_avai_days
        from listings l
        left join listing_availability la on la.listing_id=l.id
        left join (SELECT generate_series(timestamp '2023-01-18', timestamp '2023-01-31', interval '1 day')::date ymd) dates on 
        dates.ymd between la.start_date::date and la.end_date::date
        where l.status='approved' and l.deleted_at is null 
        GROUP BY 1)ola
        on ola.id = l.id
--
left join 
        (select l.id,
        count(case when (dates.ymd between '2023-01-20' and '2023-01-23') or (dates.ymd between '2023-01-27' and '2023-01-29') then dates.ymd end) as weekend_avai_days
        from listings l
        left join listing_availability la on la.listing_id=l.id
        left join (SELECT generate_series(timestamp '2023-01-18', timestamp '2023-01-31', interval '1 day')::date ymd) dates on 
        dates.ymd between la.start_date::date and la.end_date::date
        where l.status='approved' and l.deleted_at is null
        GROUP BY 1)wla
        on wla.id = l.id
where l.status = 'approved'
and l.deleted_at is null
and ((c.owner_id is null) or (l.user_id in (942862,344308,756223,31534,176936,551568,59693,120252,113801,483725,839440,760777,59551,58937,725875,797829,810417,1415199,1594773,50832,684922,1387955,548329,259352,81472,399266,79964,92561,93080,177014,89213,925742,758921,46071,1072616,1751078,82304)))
and l.registration_no in ({{ $json["String"] }})
and obj.real_rej_booking = 1 and wbj.real_rej_booking = 0
order by 10 desc

left join (select distinct listing_id, country, city_id from listing_location) ll on ll.listing_id = l.id
left join models m on m.id = l.model_id
left join companies c on c.owner_id = l.user_id
--
left join 
        (select distinct b.listing_id, 
        count(distinct case when (b.status = 'rejected' and (b.reason !~* '(guest)' or b.reason is null)) or (b.status in ('withdrawn', 'cancelled') and b.reason ~* '(host|owner|avai|car)') then b.ref_no end) as ov_rej_booking,
		count(distinct case when (b.reason = 'Host is taking a long time to respond' and ((extract(EPOCH FROM b.updated_at::timestamp) - EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM b.created_at::timestamp))/60::integer)< '20' ) then b.ref_no end)as unfair_rej_booking,
		COALESCE(count(distinct case when (b.status = 'rejected' and (b.reason !~* '(guest)' or b.reason is null)) or (b.status in ('withdrawn', 'cancelled') and b.reason ~* '(host|owner|avai|car)') then b.ref_no end) - count(distinct case when (b.reason = 'Host is taking a long time to respond' and ((extract(EPOCH FROM b.updated_at::timestamp) - EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM b.created_at::timestamp))/60::integer)< '20' ) then b.ref_no end),0) as real_rej_booking  
        from bookings b 
        where b.request_end_at::timestamp >= '2023-01-18 00:00' and b.request_start_at::timestamp <= '2023-01-31 23:59'
        group by 1)obj
        on obj.listing_id = l.id
--
left join 
        (select distinct b.listing_id, 
        count(distinct case when (b.status = 'rejected' and (b.reason !~* '(guest)' or b.reason is null)) or (b.status in ('withdrawn', 'cancelled') and b.reason ~* '(host|owner|avai|car)') then b.ref_no end) as ov_rej_booking,
		count(distinct case when (b.reason = 'Host is taking a long time to respond' and ((extract(EPOCH FROM b.updated_at::timestamp) - EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM b.created_at::timestamp))/60::integer)< '20' ) then b.ref_no end)as unfair_rej_booking,
		COALESCE(count(distinct case when (b.status = 'rejected' and (b.reason !~* '(guest)' or b.reason is null)) or (b.status in ('withdrawn', 'cancelled') and b.reason ~* '(host|owner|avai|car)') then b.ref_no end) - count(distinct case when (b.reason = 'Host is taking a long time to respond' and ((extract(EPOCH FROM b.updated_at::timestamp) - EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM b.created_at::timestamp))/60::integer)< '20' ) then b.ref_no end),0) as real_rej_booking
        from bookings b 
        where (b.request_start_at::timestamp between '2023-01-20 00:00' and '2023-01-23 23:59') or (b.request_start_at::timestamp between '2023-01-27 00:00' and '2023-01-29 23:59')
        group by 1)wbj
        on wbj.listing_id = l.id
--
left join 
        (select distinct b.listing_id, 
        count(distinct case when b.status in ('completed','start_driving','waiting_for_inspection', 'return_car','accepted') then b.id end) as overall_fuld_booking
        from bookings b 
        where b.request_end_at::timestamp >= '2023-01-18 00:00' and b.request_start_at::timestamp <= '2023-01-31 23:59'
        group by 1)obf
        on obf.listing_id = l.id
--
left join 
        (select distinct b.listing_id, 
        count(distinct case when b.status in ('completed','start_driving','waiting_for_inspection', 'return_car','accepted') then b.id end) as weekend_fuld_booking
        from bookings b 
        where (b.request_start_at::timestamp between '2023-01-20 00:00' and '2023-01-23 23:59') or (b.request_start_at::timestamp between '2023-01-27 00:00' and '2023-01-29 23:59')
        group by 1)wbf
        on wbf.listing_id = l.id
--
left join 
        (select l.id,
        count(dates.ymd) as overall_avai_days
        from listings l
        left join listing_availability la on la.listing_id=l.id
        left join (SELECT generate_series(timestamp '2023-01-18', timestamp '2023-01-31', interval '1 day')::date ymd) dates on 
        dates.ymd between la.start_date::date and la.end_date::date
        where l.status='approved' and l.deleted_at is null 
        GROUP BY 1)ola
        on ola.id = l.id
--
left join 
        (select l.id,
        count(case when (dates.ymd between '2023-01-20' and '2023-01-23') or (dates.ymd between '2023-01-27' and '2023-01-29') then dates.ymd end) as weekend_avai_days
        from listings l
        left join listing_availability la on la.listing_id=l.id
        left join (SELECT generate_series(timestamp '2023-01-18', timestamp '2023-01-31', interval '1 day')::date ymd) dates on 
        dates.ymd between la.start_date::date and la.end_date::date
        where l.status='approved' and l.deleted_at is null
        GROUP BY 1)wla
        on wla.id = l.id
where l.status = 'approved'
and l.deleted_at is null
and ((c.owner_id is null) or (l.user_id in (942862,344308,756223,31534,176936,551568,59693,120252,113801,483725,839440,760777,59551,58937,725875,797829,810417,1415199,1594773,50832,684922,1387955,548329,259352,81472,399266,79964,92561,93080,177014,89213,925742,758921,46071,1072616,1751078,82304)))
and l.registration_no in ({{ $json["String"] }})
and (wbj.real_rej_booking > 1 or obj.real_rej_booking > 2)
order by 10 desc
